In this case,

222
00:18:12,400 --> 00:18:14,160
I hope you will keep your word.

223
00:18:16,440 --> 00:18:17,800
After you have fully recovered,

224
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:20,240
you will lead your troops south

225
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:22,640
and leave the imperial city.

226
00:18:22,640 --> 00:18:26,140
♪From now on,
I am the only person to stay♪

227
00:18:26,340 --> 00:18:29,460
♪Dare not disturb.
I can only hold tightly onto memories♪

228
00:18:29,460 --> 00:18:32,100
♪How can I forget someone I've loved?♪

229
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:34,940
♪It's impossible to return to before♪

230
00:18:36,420 --> 00:18:43,100
♪Tell me, how do we settle our regrets?♪

231
00:18:43,100 --> 00:18:49,300
♪Because I loved you too much,
I let go of my pride♪

232
00:18:50,140 --> 00:18:55,620
♪I can't learn to leave you so easily♪

233
00:18:55,620 --> 00:18:58,820
♪You left with just a goodbye♪

234
00:18:58,820 --> 00:19:04,260
♪Letting me linger in the same spot,
heartache for years♪

235
00:19:04,260 --> 00:19:07,420
♪From then on, I lost you♪

